kpi_info.title: Failed call setup attempts
kpi_info.use: Number of failed call setup attempts that have terminated in a normal release. The counter is updated when the call is interrupted during the setup phase, and the clear code is in the range of 001-3FF. It means that the MSC either receives the CM_SERVICE_ABORT message, receives or sends the BSSAP RELEASE COMPLETE message, receives or sends the CC RELEASE COMPLETE message, or receives the ISUP Release Complete or the ISUP Release message from the other exchange.
